	   	"title":"深圳中学2016届高考报告",
	   	"content":"\t深圳中学致力于让优秀者更优秀，让平常者不平常。在大批优秀学生被国外名校录取的情况下，我校今年高考取得了优异的成绩。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n1、广东省高考总分前十名深圳中学有2人（总分被屏蔽）。<br />\n广东省理科总分前十名：高三（1）班李泽远。<br />\n广东省文科总分前十名：高三（18）班郭家杰。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n2、深圳中学高考一本率达到94.09%，本科率达到100%。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 参加高考人数 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;达一本线人数 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;一本率 &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n普通理科生 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;586 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;550 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;93.86%<br />\n普通文科生 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;137 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;130 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;94.89%<br />\n艺术体育生 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 5 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;5 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;100%<br />\n合计 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;728 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;685 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;94.09%<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n3、广东省理科总分前300名，深中32人，人数位列全省第一。其中前100名，深中9人；前200名，深中18人。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n4、广东省文科总分前300名，深中21人，人数位列全省第一。其中前50名，深中6人；前100名，深中8人；前200名，深中13人。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n5、深圳中学2016届高三预计有23人被北大、清华录取。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n6、深圳中学文理各段高分人数占全市比率：<br />\n理科 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;省前100名 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;省前200名 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;省前300名 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 省前400名 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;省前500名<br />\n深圳中学 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;9 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;18 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 32 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;37 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;46<br />\n深圳市其他学校合计  &nbsp; &nbsp; 9 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;17 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;21 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;27 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;40<br />\n深圳市合计 &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;18 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 35 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;53 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 64 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;86<br />\n深圳中学占比  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;50% &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;51% &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;60% &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;58% &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 53%<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n文科 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;省前50名 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 省前100名 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 省前200名 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 省前300名 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;省前400名<br />\n深圳中学 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;6 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 8 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;13 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 21 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 24<br />\n深圳市其他学校合计  &nbsp; 4 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 8 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;18 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 34 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 44<br />\n深圳市合计 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;10 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;16 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;31 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 55 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 68<br />\n深圳中学占比  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;60% &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 50% &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 42% &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;38% &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;35%<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n7、深圳中学总分600分以上人数：理科257人，文科23人。<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 今年深圳中学国际体系有143名同学被排名前五十的美国大学录取，录取比例超过90%，其中13位同学被排名前十的美国综合性大学、文理学院和艺术院校录取，72位同学被排名前三十的美国大学录取。此外还有多名学生被牛津大学等海外名校录取。<br />\n在此，向2016届高三年级全体毕业生表示祝贺，向2016届高三年级全体教职员工表示感谢，向支持深中工作的各级领导、学生家长和社会各界表示感谢！",
