		"content":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:center;\">\t<b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;\">深圳中学中国科学技术大学<span>2017</span>年少年班<span></span></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:center;\">\t<b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;\">“创新试点班”招生办法<span></span></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:justify;text-indent:21pt;\">\t<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:justify;text-indent:21pt;\">\t<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:24px;font-family:宋体;\">中国科学技术大学<span>2017</span>年少年班“创新试点班”计划</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:24px;font-family:宋体;\">现正启动，中科大给予深中<span>7</span>个校荐名额。经相关老师商讨，现重新修订报名条件，启动第二次报名。有意报考的同学可于<b><span>10</span>月<span>14</span>日（周五）<span>17</span>：<span>00</span>前到<span>D110</span>周爽老师</b>处登记报名。<span></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:justify;text-indent:24pt;\">\t<span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:24px;font-family:宋体;\">报名选拔条件如下：<span></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:justify;text-indent:24pt;\">\t<span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:24px;font-family:宋体;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:24px;font-family:宋体;\">学分积点<b><span style=\"color:red;\">4.3</span><span style=\"color:red;\">（含）</span></b>以上的理科同学；<span></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:justify;text-indent:6pt;\">\t<span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:24px;font-family:宋体;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:24px;font-family:宋体;\">符合条件<span>1</span>者，按五大学科竞赛成绩择优推荐；<span></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:justify;text-indent:23.9pt;\">\t<span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:24px;font-family:宋体;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:24px;font-family:宋体;\">竞赛成绩同等者，按高一第二学期期末考试六科（语数英理化生）总分排名择优推荐。<span></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\">\t<span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:24px;font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" align=\"right\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:right;text-indent:0cm;\">\t<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\">升学指导中心<span></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" align=\"right\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:right;text-indent:0cm;\">\t<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\">2016.10.8</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">\t<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">\t<b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:red;\">附：</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:'????', serif;color:red;\"></span></b></p><div align=\"center\" style=\"font-family:Simsun;font-size:medium;\">\t<table class=\"MsoNormalTable ke-zeroborder\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"700\" style=\"width:525pt;\">\t\t<tbody>\t\t\t<tr>\t\t\t\t<td>\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-align:center;\">\t\t\t\t\t\t<b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#383838;\">中国科学技术大学</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:'????', serif;color:#383838;\">2017</span></b><b><span sty