		"content":"<p>\t<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">\t\t<b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:宋体;color:red;\">香港科技大学招生官访问我校</span></b>\t</p>\t<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">\t\t<span style=\"font-size:15pt;\">&nbsp;</span>\t</p>\t<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-indent:30pt;\">\t\t<span style=\"font-size:15pt;\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:15pt;font-family:宋体;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:15pt;\">17</span><span style=\"font-size:15pt;font-family:宋体;\">日下午香港科技大学招生官团队访问我校，将针对高考和国际方向同学同时进行两场招生讲座。届时将介绍港科大</span><span style=\"font-size:15pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:15pt;font-family:宋体;\">学校情况、升学概况、入取标准和解答各位同学的相关问题。请有志于报考港科大的同学和感兴趣的同学参加。</span>\t</p>\t<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">\t\t<span style=\"font-size:15pt;font-family:宋体;\">时间：</span><span style=\"font-size:15pt;\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:15pt;font-family:宋体;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:15pt;\">17</span><span style=\"font-size:15pt;font-family:宋体;\">号，星期一</span><span style=\"font-size:15pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:15pt;font-family:宋体;\">下午</span><span style=\"font-size:15pt;\">4:50-5:50</span>\t</p>\t<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">\t\t<span style=\"font-size:15pt;font-family:宋体;\">地点：</span>\t</p>\t<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-indent:37.5pt;\">\t\t<span style=\"font-size:15pt;font-family:宋体;\">国际方向（通过</span><span style=\"font-size:15pt;\">SAT/ACT,A-Level</span><span style=\"font-size:15pt;font-family:宋体;\">考试申请）：</span><span style=\"font-size:15pt;\">D505</span>\t</p>\t<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-indent:37.5pt;\">\t\t<span style=\"font-size:15pt;font-family:宋体;\">高考方向（通过高考申请）：</span><span style=\"font-size:15pt;\">C308</span>\t</p>\t<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">\t\t<span style=\"font-size:15pt;\">&nbsp;</span>\t</p>\t<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">\t\t<span style=\"font-size:15pt;\">&nbsp;</span>\t</p>\t<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">\t\t<span style=\"font-size:15pt;font-family:宋体;\">升学指导中心</span>\t</p>\t<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">\t\t<span>2016/10/16</span>\t</p></p>"
