;&nbsp;</span>高二<span>18</span></span>\t</p>\t<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:20.9pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">\t\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white;\">公示期自<span>2016</span>年<span>10</span>月<span>16</span>日至<span>18</span>日，共<span>3</span>天。对以上人员有任何疑问，请与升学指导中心马老师联系，联系电话<span>82155710</span>。</span>\t</p>\t<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">\t\t<span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:24px;font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;</span>\t</p>\t<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right;text-indent:0cm;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">\t\t<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\">升学指导中心</span>\t</p>\t<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right;text-indent:0cm;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">\t\t<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\">2016.10.15</span>\t</p>\t<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">\t\t<span>&nbsp;</span>\t</p></p>"
	
